  "instructions": [
    "In a large pan, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the grated carrot and chopped spinach, cook for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the cooked vegetables, ground oats, cumin, coriander powder, cayenne pepper, salt, and pepper.",
    "Mix well until the oats are evenly coated with the spices.",
    "To assemble the wraps, lay the tortilla flat and add a large spoonful of the oat mixture.",
    "Fold the bottom half of the tortilla up over the filling, then fold in the sides and roll the wrap up tightly.",
    "Repeat with the remaining filling and tortillas.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
